DOC.brief_summary: Effects on weight will be monitored in healthy infant subjects consuming assigned infant formulas.
DOC.brief_title: Growth of Infants Fed an Elemental Medical Food
DOC.criteria: Singleton, healthy infant Gestational age of 37 to 42 weeks Birth weight of 2500 grams or greater Age between birth and 9 days of age Parents agree to not administer mineral or vitamin supplements during the study period Parents agree to feed study formula exclusively for the duration of the study Maternal, fetal or perinatal history which may have adverse effects on growth Multiple birth
